# Scope Guardrails (v1)
rules:
  - name: "Preflight Scope Check"
    trigger: "Preflight scope"
    instructions: |
      1) Read scripts/verify_changed_files.sh and .github/PULL_REQUEST_TEMPLATE.md.
      2) Refuse to write outside ALLOWED_PATHS. If a user requests broader scope, ask for confirmation.
      3) If uncertain, propose a plan and request which paths to allow.
